dramatic thriller debra winger plays a detective who is on the trail of a psychopathic woman . she quickly meets , `` falls in love '' and then marries her man , but soon kills him before moving onto the next man repeating the process all over again . when the detective finally locates her in hawaii , she meets her and the two become friends . as she investigates the woman 's web of lies and murder , the woman becomes suspicious of her . when she finally discovers that her friend is a detective , it becomes a deadly rollercoaster ride as she repeatedly tries to kill her . some of the best scenes were ... poisoning the wine scene , the scuba-diving scene , the scalding shower scene , and the end scene